BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-05T23:45:00&endDate=2026-06-08T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nPICCADILLY LINE: Saturday 6 June\, from 0045\, and all day Sunday 7 June\, no service between Hammersmith and Heathrow (All Terminals) / Uxbridge\, including Friday and Saturday Night Tube. Use METROPOLITAN LINE services between Rayners Lane and Uxbridge.
